00:22:45.597 --> 00:22:47.032
[GOKU]
Hey! It's me--Goku!

00:22:47.066 --> 00:22:50.206
Wow, helping people out sure
is keeping you busy, Gohan!

00:22:50.239 --> 00:22:51.374
[GOHAN]
What can I say, Dad?

00:22:51.408 --> 00:22:53.011
Being a superhero
is a full-time job!

00:22:53.044 --> 00:22:55.282
[VIDEL] You may look like you
stumbled through a costume shop,

00:22:55.315 --> 00:22:58.590
Great Saiyaman, but there's
